    <p id="_bookmark177">ABS</p>
    <p>
      <b>ABS</b>
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>描述 </b>计算一个数字的绝对值。</p>
    <p>
      <fig>
        <image href="../graphics/PaaS_Business_Model_Design_and_Management_V2104_01_topic47_image001.png" />
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>使用 </b>ABS(number)</p>
    <p>返回值为整数型或者实数型。</p>
    <p>
      <table>
        <tgroup cols="1" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
          <colspec colname="c1" align="left" />
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry colname="c1">
                <image href="../graphics/PaaS_Business_Model_Design_and_Management_V2104_01_topic47_image001.png" />
              </entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </table>
 number 为整数、实数型字段或者其他要计算的数值。</p>
    <p>
      <b>样例 </b>ABS(-7.7) 此公式返回结果为 7.7 ABS(-7) 此公式返回结果为 7</p>
    <p>
      <fig>
        <image href="../graphics/PaaS_Business_Model_Design_and_Management_V2104_01_topic47_image001.png" />
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>
      <table>
        <tgroup cols="1" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
          <colspec colname="c1" align="left" />
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry colname="c1">
                <image href="../graphics/PaaS_Business_Model_Design_and_Management_V2104_01_topic47_image002.png" />
              </entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </table>
 注意点 无</p>
    <p id="_bookmark179">Ceiling</p>
    <p>
      <b>Ceiling</b>
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>描述 </b>将一个数字向上取整，即取整为大于等于自身的最小整数。</p>
    <p>
      <fig>
        <image href="../graphics/PaaS_Business_Model_Design_and_Management_V2104_01_topic47_image001.png" />
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>使用 </b>CEILING(number) 返回值为实数型。</p>
    <p>
      <table>
        <tgroup cols="1" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
          <colspec colname="c1" align="left" />
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry colname="c1">
                <image href="../graphics/PaaS_Business_Model_Design_and_Management_V2104_01_topic47_image001.png" />
              </entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </table>
 number 为整数、实数型字段或者其他要计算的数值。</p>
    <p>
      <b>样例 </b>Ceiling(7.1) 此公式返回结果为 8.0 Ceiling(-7.75) 此公式返回结果为
 -7.0</p>
    <p>
      <fig>
        <image href="../graphics/PaaS_Business_Model_Design_and_Management_V2104_01_topic47_image001.png" />
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>
      <table>
        <tgroup cols="1" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
          <colspec colname="c1" align="left" />
          <tbody>
            <row>
              <entry colname="c1">
                <image href="../graphics/PaaS_Business_Model_Design_and_Management_V2104_01_topic47_image002.png" />
              </entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </table>
      <b>注意点 </b>此函数取整时不进行四舍五入，直接向上取整。</p>
    <p id="_bookmark181">LN</p>
    <p>
      <b>LN</b>
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>描述 </b>计算一个数字的自然对数。</p>
    <p>
      <fig>
        <image href="../graphics/PaaS_Business_Model_Design_and_Management_V2104_01_topic47_image001.png" />
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p>
      <b>使用 </b>LN(number)</p>
    <p>返回值为实数型。</p>
    <p>
      <table>
        <tgroup cols="1" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
