                <fig>
                  <image href="../graphics/PaaS_Business_Model_Design_and_Management_V2104_01_topic47_image002.png" />
                </fig>
              </entry>
            </row>
          </tbody>
        </tgroup>
      </table>
      <b>注意点 </b>此函数取整时不进行四舍五入，直接向下取整。</p>
